2015-10-27 07:58  doug

	* usr.sbin/nsd/: nsd-control.c, remote.c: Fix nsd and unbound's
	  error checking with SSL_CTX_set_options().

	  LibreSSL, BoringSSL and OpenSSL have all been redefining SSL_OP_*
	  flags to be 0 when support is removed.  This breaks the error
	  checking that nsd and unbound were doing.  It should check
	  against the flag value itself to allow for 0.

	  input deraadt@, jsing@ tweak + ok miod@, guenther@

